replies.body:
Ok, good idea. However, heres my problem with that: {{item:3124}}
Wouldn't this just fundamentally break your idea in seconds?
Im also not fond of giving adcs more damage and shields (PD and Enchanters are already enough to make me sick). Giving them armor pen just makes them even more of a problem for tanks to deal with. It would take them from countering tanks to completely nullifying tanks. Im trying to get rid of the nullifying issue, and crit is a part of it.
